708
00:37:28,980 --> 00:37:30,060
Given my status,

709
00:37:30,780 --> 00:37:31,700
it's not appropriate.

710
00:37:34,020 --> 00:37:35,300
Since we're family,

711
00:37:35,420 --> 00:37:36,660
I'll just be straightforward.

712
00:37:37,660 --> 00:37:38,870
You know

713
00:37:38,870 --> 00:37:39,940
