714
00:37:39,940 --> 00:37:41,560
We can't afford to spend a lot of money.

715
00:37:41,580 --> 00:37:42,700
But altogether,

716
00:37:42,700 --> 00:37:45,260
we've managed to gather
600 taels of silver.

717
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:47,220
Donglin contributed 200 taels,

718
00:37:47,340 --> 00:37:48,620
Sixi contributed 200 taels,

719
00:37:48,620 --> 00:37:50,300
the family contributed 100 taels,

720
00:37:50,420 --> 00:37:51,620
and the remaining hundred taels

721
00:37:51,620 --> 00:37:52,820
