724
00:37:59,340 --> 00:38:00,580
I have to say it.

725
00:38:00,700 --> 00:38:01,940
I can't let you give the money

726
00:38:02,100 --> 00:38:03,460
into the shadows.

727
00:38:04,260 --> 00:38:06,060
Madam, let me make this clear.

728
00:38:06,220 --> 00:38:08,060
I saved 100 taels of silver.

729
00:38:08,180 --> 00:38:09,780
It's not taken from the family.

730
00:38:10,260 --> 00:38:11,180
You have money.

731
00:38:11,180 --> 00:38:12,260
You're a wealthy woman.

732
00:38:12,940 --> 00:38:14,300
Of course, I want

733
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:16,060
to contribute to Aji's wedding.

734
00:38:23,180 --> 00:38:24,100
Mother,

735
00:38:24,660 --> 00:38:25,580
Muyun,

736
00:38:27,140 --> 00:38:30,420
I think 600 taels is too much.

737
00:38:31,780 --> 00:38:32,860
Our family

738
00:38:33,300 --> 00:38:35,540
needs money right now.

739
00:38:35,940 --> 00:38:37,100
- How about...
- Stop.

740
00:38:37,500 --> 00:38:39,100
Now, I'm in charge.

741
00:38:39,340 --> 00:38:40,900
This matter is settled.

742
00:38:41,860 --> 00:38:44,020
Besides, if we give less,

743
00:38:44,020 --> 00:38:45,820
where would

744
00:38:45,820 --> 00:38:46,740
Chief Luo's face be?

745
00:38:47,340 --> 00:38:48,460
Don't make fun of me.

746
00:38:49,420 --> 00:38:51,380
I'm no longer the Chief.

747
00:38:51,860 --> 00:38:53,300
Alright, let's not talk about it.

748
00:38:53,780 --> 00:38:56,100
Aji grew up under my watch.

749
00:38:56,540 --> 00:38:58,220
600 it is.

750
00:39:01,540 --> 00:39:03,540
You two have work to do
this afternoon, right?

751
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:04,980
Don't even think about it.

752
00:39:04,980 --> 00:39:06,180
There's a pile of things to do.

753
00:39:06,300 --> 00:39:07,780
What else is there?

754
00:39:08,660 --> 00:39:10,360
The incense
in the ancestral hall is gone.

755
00:39:10,380 --> 00:39:11,580
The trees need watering.

756
00:39:11,740 --> 00:39:13,020
Dinner hasn't been prepared.

757
00:39:13,020 --> 00:39:14,700
- Right.
- We need to make potstickers.

758
00:39:14,860 --> 00:39:16,740
Then let's hurry up.

